<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_92e960fd-431e-438a-8719-025ad168976d" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>A1G3</sptc><title id="_a6b0a58f-b3dc-4b49-9f51-21af37404d6d">Scope of NCC Volume Three</title><archive-num>New for 2022</archive-num><subclause id="_6aaebb68-5275-4000-9c67-0b8d5848d518" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_cb70a529-0e9a-4e47-83ff-6a104f8d78e3">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>NCC Volume Three contains technical requirements for the design, construction, installation, replacement, repair, alteration and maintenance for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1401_0.7.0.xml#_a318c0f3-5635-4ac0-b103-59d798c9f23d" id="_41637bc6-7242-4d69-80ca-c91e085c0209" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">plumbing</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1249_0.8.0.xml#_25307451-c7e1-4167-b4de-e5a1af26694c" id="_381a6cbf-3de4-4e96-aa73-b43d100662a2" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">drainage</xref> systems in new and existing buildings.</p></subclause><subclause id="_0c6a425a-1c4e-41cc-9ec5-c714d153e570" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_a9989eea-c07b-4712-8133-feef7a1c65e6">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>NCC Volume Three applies to these systems in all classes of buildings whenever <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1401_0.7.0.xml#_a318c0f3-5635-4ac0-b103-59d798c9f23d" id="_2b52b32f-b869-48ce-8c87-8589869b5978" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">plumbing</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1249_0.8.0.xml#_25307451-c7e1-4167-b4de-e5a1af26694c" id="_8760fdff-0c87-4596-b575-c13014a7616f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">drainage</xref> work is carried out.</p></subclause><subclause id="_86f0f32c-8930-4c59-b779-1169c33c2d6e" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_94d55733-0348-4930-a33a-95ad3de82867">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>NCC Volume Three additionally applies to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1463_0.4.0.xml#_fb3536f6-7ee5-4a29-a4da-402a8e1168dc" id="_a983f0aa-70f3-4108-b107-f6a2ebd7eab2" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">sites</xref> where services are designed, constructed, installed, replaced, repaired, altered and maintained independently of buildings.</p></subclause><subclause id="_f1b48988-9b1a-4e78-90a6-623f7a912ca3" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_6d2eba35-5255-4ec1-9120-fb884fbdf504">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>NCC Volume Three applies from the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1403_3.12.0.xml#_7df493b5-1832-40a0-b9d0-d2fb3fec5d98" id="_7fdc8c00-4c6a-4a82-ab26-e61aeb0e58f3" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">point of connection</xref> to the point of discharge.</p></subclause></clause>